cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.SOC, cs.LG, cs.HC 

This paper is primarily concerned with improving recommendation systems by incorporating social information. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Additionally, the paper discusses social networks and their dynamics, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.SOC (Social and Information Networks). The paper also proposes novel recommendation approaches, which could place it in cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
